item.title: Projects
item.description: This is a list of my current projects that I’m involved in one way or another. Proxmox VE Server This very website runs on a Proxmox VE server maintained in my home. If you’re curious, the specifications are below: Dell Poweredge R430 2 x Intel Xeon E5-2640 V4 192GB DDR4-2133 240GB RAID1 1.2TB RAID1 12TB SINGLE DRIVE 8 x 1G NIC This is the server that I use for homelabbing purposes, doing everything from running my network with OPNsense to miscellaneous Docker and LXC containers.
